1. to visually test rng for pairwise independence

   $ cd path/to/kalman
   $ nix-shell
   $ xterm
   ..in xterm window..
   $ cd build
   $ ./example > tmp.txt
   # at menu enter '2' for uniformly-distributed random #'s
   > 2
   $ gnuplot
   gnuplot> set terminal xterm
   gnuplot> plot "tmp.txt" with points pointtype 7 pointsize 0 lc "blue" notitle
   